com.interpss.simu.multicase.rule

Interface RuleSet

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RuleSetImpl

    public interface RuleSet
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Rule Set'. Class for defining RuleSet. RuleBase --(*) RuleSet --(*) Rule. It contains a set of Bus action rules and/or a set of branch action rules. A rule set has a priority and and a rule type (preventive or corrective)

    The following features are supported:

    • Priority
    • Rule Type
    • Bus Action Rules
    • Branch Action Rules
    See Also:
    MCaseRulePackage.getRuleSet()
